  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [NON-ENGLISH] is, I mean, is not a full Jew, it's a small Jew, a [NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's-- a little Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that's--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is-- is-- they got to tell you, I mean, it's something, they won't tell you something, you have [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It mean you're a Jew or something like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It's a special explanation, Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can't explain-- [LAUGHS] You can't translate, the [POLISH] to Jewish, in Polish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's so how-- anyway, in 1939, they first start the war again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That start the regular war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then start the big trouble.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 1st of September, I was in Warsaw at this time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the army, our army--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We was in the-- in the units, so army units.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some there--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The army just-- those stationed there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Stationed there or something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the city was bombarded day and night for two weeks, without end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the end-- this, the army, when they can go out they go out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was on the-- I went out with the-- with the unit, what they call is-- in German was a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is armored-- armored trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they tell all soldiers what they can take it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They think they form a new army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the army was destroyed in the West.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were forming a new army on the Bug.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Bug is in East Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in this go from north to down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And over there they think they go back over there they can form.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they got reserves, can make a new Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember The division was-- was a mixture of all-- all soldiers what runaway.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
